Dandelion DX dashboard

Data Considerations

  • 20 random ACP samples from each diagnosis were used, for the sake of computing power.
  • The processing pipeline was the following:
    • Cut x-axis [500, 2600]
    • rp.preprocessing.baseline.IASLS(diff_order=3)
    • rp.preprocessing.normalise.MinMax()
  • The plots show the average and standard deviation between all samples, 3 replicates (r) and 3 points (p).
